})();</script><style> .page-features .nav-features { border-bottom-color: #f56727; } </style></head><body class="page-features"><div class="site-wrapper"><!--[if lt IE 8 ]><section class="info-bar align-center"><p>To use this website properly, please, use a more recent version of Internet Explorer.</p></section><![endif]--><header><h1><a href="./">HTML<sup>5</sup> Shopping Cart</a></h1><ul><li><a href="http://wemakesites.net/" target="_blank">About</a></li><li><a href="https://twitter.com/wemakesitesnet" target="_blank">@wemakesitesnet</a></li><li><a href="http://acidmartin.wordpress.com/" target="_blank">Blog</a></li><li><a href="http://wemakesites.net/#!/contact" target="_blank">Contact</a></li></ul></header><nav><ul><li><a href="./" class="nav-default-page">Home</a></li><li><a href="features.html" class="nav-features">Features</a></li><li><a href="download.html" class="nav-download">Download</a></li><li><a href="licensing.html" class="nav-licensing">Licensing</a></li><li><a href="demo.html" class="nav-demo">Demo</a></li><li><a href="purchase.html" class="nav-purchase">Purchase</a></li><li><a href="documentation.html" class="nav-documentation">API</a></li></ul><div class="checkout-placeholder"><div class="acidjs-shopping-cart-dropdown"><!-- / --></div></div></nav><div class="site-content"><noscript>This website as well as HTML5 Cart make heavy use of JavaScript, which is disabled in your browser. For complete experience, please, enable JavaScript and reload the page.</noscript><h2>HTML5 Cart Features</h2><section><h3 class="icons-32 icons-independent">Platform-independent</h3><p><strong class="logo">HTML<sup>5</sup> Cart</strong> operates fully in the browser, and does not depend on the type of the web-server you are using.</p><h3 class="icons-32 icons-html5">HTML5, CSS3 and JavaScript Driven</h3><p>Amazingly fast and responsive. Built with best practices and latest development trends in mind.</p><h3 class="icons-32 icons-configure">Powerful Build Tools</h3><p>Each commercial <a href="licensing.html">license</a> of <strong class="logo">HTML<sup>5</sup> Cart</strong> comes with free access to our online state-of-the-art <a href="editor.html">HTML5-driven editor</a>, which allows you easy creation or modification or shopping cart data files straight into your favorite browser. The Developer <a href="licensing.html">license</a> comes with powerful JavaScript and CSS optimization and minification tools.</p><h3 class="icons-32 icons-payment-gateway">Support for Different Payment Gateways</h3><p>Currently, the small business and enterprise <a href="licensing.html">licenses</a> come with one payment provider - PayPal, but we are working on support for Google Checkout and Amazon Payments. The basic version of <strong class="logo">HTML<sup>5</sup> Cart</strong> does not include a payment provider, but you can easily create one, using our API, which allows the integration of any payment provider. For more information about payment providers, please, check our <a href="documentation.html#heading-payment-providers">Documentation and API page</a>.</p><h3 class="icons-32 icons-elegant">Lightweight and Elegant</h3><p>The entire <strong class="logo">HTML<sup>5</sup> Cart</strong> (CSS, JavaScript and template files) is just about 40KB minified and g-zipped.</p><h3 class="icons-32 icons-templates">External Templates</h3><p>If you know HTML and CSS you can easily change the looks and the rendering of <strong class="logo">HTML<sup>5</sup> Cart</strong>.</p><h3 class="icons-32 icons-currency">International Currency Support</h3><p><strong class="logo">HTML<sup>5</sup> Cart</strong> will support any currency, supported by the selected <a href="documentation.html#heading-payment-providers">payment provider</a>. It will also add automatically the currency symbol (if available) along with the currency code.</p><h3 class="icons-32 icons-licenses">Flexible Licenses</h3><p>We provide flexible and affordable licenses for any businesses. For more information, please, check our <a href="licensing.html">licenses page</a>.</p><h3 class="icons-32 icons-browsers">Supported Browsers:</h3><ul class="multipurpose-list browsers-list"><li class="icons-16 icons-ff">Mozilla Firefox</li><li class="icons-16 icons-gc">Google Chrome</li><li class="icons-16 icons-as">Apple Safari</li><li class="icons-16 icons-op">Opera</li><li class="icons-16 icons-ie">Internet Explorer 8+ (but still working with IE6/7)</li></ul><h3 class="icons-32 icons-add-to-cart-buttons">Add to Cart Buttons</h3><p>If you do not want to use the "shop" mode of <strong class="logo">HTML<sup>5</sup> Cart</strong>, you can associate the items you sell on your website with our <a href="documentation.html#add-to-cart-buttons">add to cart buttons</a>. This can done extremely easy, and any license of <strong class="logo">HTML<sup>5</sup> Cart</strong> is shipped with 5 ready to use add to cart buttons. Moreover, you can easily create your own buttons with CSS.</p><h3 class="icons-32 icons-configure">Easy to Install, Configure and Run.</h3><p>No data bases and server setup - just pure client-side implementation. Basically, what you need to do is adding a few JavaScript and CSS files, defining a few configuration properties and include your items to a simple JSON file. Please, check the <a href="documentation.html">documentation</a> for a jump start using <strong class="logo">HTML<sup>5</sup> Cart</strong>.</p><h3 class="icons-32 icons-modes">Modes</h3><p><strong class="logo">HTML<sup>5</sup> Cart</strong> supports two operation modes - <code>"cart"</code> (default) and <code>"shop"</code>. Please, check our <a href="documentation.html#configuring-html5-cart">documentation</a> page for more info about modes.</p><h3 class="icons-32 icons-lang">Localizable</h3><p>The current version of <strong class="logo">HTML<sup>5</sup> Cart</strong> comes with English and Bulgarian languages, but creating a <a href="documentation.html#heading-localization">language file</a> is a matter of minutes - all you have to do is to edit a simple JSON file.</p><h3 class="icons-32 icons-modes">Support for Multiple Data Files in Cross-platform JSON Format.</h3><p>You can have different shopping carts on a single website. Please, check our <a href="documentation.html#cart-items-data-files">documentation</a>.</p><h3 class="icons-32 icons-themes">Themes</h3><p>The support for themes is currently under development and will be released soon.</p></section><section><div class="acidjs-shopping-cart"><!-- / --></div></section></div><footer><ul><li>&copy;2013</li><li><a href="http://wemakesites.net/" target="_blank">About</a></li><li><a href="https://twitter.com/wemakesitesnet" target="_blank">@wemakesitesnet</a></li><li><a href="http://acidmartin.wordpress.com/" target="_blank">Blog</a></li><li><a href="http://wemakesites.net/#!/contact" target="_blank">Contact</a></li></ul></footer></div><script src="server/load-js.php?files=..%2Flib%2Fjson2%2Fjson2.js"></script><script src="server/load-js.php?files=..%2Flib%2FjQuery%2Fjquery-1.9.1.min.js"></script><script src="server/load-js.php?files=..%2FAcidJs.ShoppingCart%2Fclasses%2FShoppingCart.min.js"></script><script src="server/load-js.php?files=../classes/site.min.js"></script><script> (function() { "use strict"; window.site = new AcidJs.Site({ page: "features", debug: false, cartConfig: null }); })(); </script></body></html>